{"title":"小L的牧场","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":128,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/273#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=273","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/273/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/273/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/273"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"　　小L在老家买了很大一块儿地来养羊，为了不让这些羊到处乱跑，小L需要把这些羊用栅栏围起来。这些羊在他的地里有自己固定的吃草地点，所以栅栏的范围必须包含这些点 ( 可以与栅栏重合 )，小L希望花费尽可能少的栅栏，请你帮忙计算小L最少需要多长的栅栏。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行一个整数n表示这些羊的固定吃草点  \r\n接下来n行每行两个实数描述一个点的坐标 **( 可能为浮点数 )**"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出一行一个浮点数，表示最短的栅栏长度，**保留两位小数**"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"####输入样例\r\n```\r\n4\r\n4 8\r\n4 12\r\n5 9.3\r\n7 8 \r\n```\r\n####输出样例\r\n```\r\n12.00\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"0 <= n <= 10000  \r\n-1000000 <=  x, y <= 1000000"}]}